---
title: Harissa-Honey Double Pork Chops with Herby Couscous Pilaf and Creamy Lemon Sauce
description: Juicy pork chops are given a bold flavour boost of Harissa Spice Blend and honey to complement a harmonious blend of almonds, raisins, mint, spinach and bell pepper in a light and fluffy couscous pilaf.
